{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9bea0bfbc9","title":"成都工学院学生反对党的领导的言论","origin":"《右派言论选集》（中共成都工学院委员会办公室，1957年）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6f9065a28f","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"9bea0bfbc9"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"1a846fc0a8","name":"曹振东"},{"id":"49dc136d28","name":"马骊"},{"id":"4c0546f58a","name":"成都工学院"},{"id":"5fe7b40c2a","name":"罗孝德"},{"id":"b5d8d3d662","name":"周懋政"},{"id":"c6ea7dd029","name":"邓安松"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"76e570ff1c","type":"title","text":"成都工学院学生反对党的领导的言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9bea0bfbc9"},{"id":"165c45b312","type":"authors","text":"成都工学院周懋政邓安松罗孝德曹振东马骊","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9bea0bfbc9"},{"id":"3f142772fb","type":"paragraph","text":"“主张教授治校：教授是内行，管理学校较好；教授治校可减轻政治课和平时政治学习，会更多的强调学术。对党的一些方针如节约等，可以不象党委抓得那样紧”。(周懋政)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9bea0bfbc9"},{"id":"686a01477e","type":"paragraph","text":"“外行不能领导内行。”(邓安松)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9bea0bfbc9"},{"id":"7263979ebe","type":"paragraph","text":"“共产党要民主党派拿出保密文件就得拿出来，如果民主党派叫共产党拿，共产党就不拿出来。”(邓安松)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9bea0bfbc9"},{"id":"e9bcceafd2","type":"paragraph","text":"“我们周围有便衣警察。”(邓安松)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9bea0bfbc9"},{"id":"158e9e9a88","type":"paragraph","text":"“学校是搞科学的机关。”“他妈的两个院长都是白条，吃政治饭的，学术都不懂能领导学校吗？”(罗孝德)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9bea0bfbc9"},{"id":"087f7ace23","type":"paragraph","text":"“四川大学竟有这样一个敢作敢为的人(指冯元春)，成都工学院都没有这样一个人，也许是我们院党委的领导太‘英明、伟大’了。”(罗孝德)","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9bea0bfbc9"},{"id":"d8e8f5bbac","type":"paragraph","text":"“文艺为工农是倒退、教条、公式化、概念化，没有人情味，没有人性。”“对藏胞歌颂解放军一歌，特别反对，因为他歌颂了领袖，听起来都不安逸”。(曹振东)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9bea0bfbc9"},{"id":"199f591bc3","type":"paragraph","text":"“成立行动委员会，领导班上鸣放，与别班取得联系，与党委谈判”。(马骊)","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9bea0bfbc9"},{"id":"920a013e2d","type":"paragraph","text":"“学校党委最不民主，胆小怕事，主张在提意见时，更尖锐更好。”(马骊)","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9bea0bfbc9"},{"id":"5bf019a857","type":"paragraph","text":"“学校领导方面都不懂教育事业，而白吃饭。这是不对的，是外行应排除。”(电56甲鸣者)","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9bea0bfbc9"}],"page":{"id":"b7ea3924c7","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9bea0bfbc9","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}